Name: Super Kiwi 64
About the game: Super Kiwi 64 is a 3D-Platformer and Collect-a-Thon, in a low poly late 90s console look. Features: - Low poly late 90s retro looks. - Kiwi can jump, glide, corkscrew-attack and stick to walls in order to jump up almost every wall. - The levels can be played in any order, and not every level needs to be finished in order to collect enough to reach the ending. - Features a bird with a long beak!
